<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870812-0127 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:Reverse Split ApprovedFor Landmark American</HL><DD> 08/12/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> LCODIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><DATELINE> MARIETTA, Ga.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Landmark American Corp., formerly Landmark Technologies Corp., said its shareholders approved a 1-for-2 1/2 reverse stock split, effective yesterday to holders of record Aug. 10.    The reverse split reduced the number of shares outstanding to about 4.9 million, the historic-rehabilitation and urban-redevelopment concern said.    Holders also approved the name change to Landmark American, effective immediately, the company said. </TEXT></DOC>